de.hsos.ecs.richwps.wpsmonitor.control

Class MeasureJobListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.hsos.ecs.richwps.wpsmonitor.control.MeasureJobListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.quartz.JobListener

    public class MeasureJobListener
extends Object
implements org.quartz.JobListener
    Evaluates if a job can't be measured because of an exception. In addition, the listener fires its own event over the MonitorEventHandler: scheduler.job.wasexecuted with the process entity as message if a job was executed and scheduler.job.paused with the process entity as message if a job cant measure a wps process.
    Author:
    Florian Vogelpohl
